window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Caina is a ghost nightfighter, one of the emperor’s elite spies and assassins, and few enemies of the empire ever escape her cunning.&nbsp;</p> <p>Yet all Caina’s wit and skill might not be enough to save her from a terrible fate.&nbsp;</p> <p>Sent to hunt down a cruel slave trader, Caina encounters something far darker. An ancient evil, a thing of legend and terror.&nbsp;</p> <p>A creature that wants to corrupt her, heart and soul....</p>"; 
